wikipedia_page.main: Henry Page (born 16 November 1788 at Cambridge; date of death unknown) was an English professional cricketer who played first-class cricket from 1819 to 1826.  He was mainly associated with Cambridge Town Club and made 7 known appearances in first-class matches.
